OL,6,FCases of hypertension and chronic
OL,7,Fkidney disease are projected to
OL,8,Fincrease by 3,280 and 1,000
OL,9,Frespectively over the next two decades.
OL,11,FThese increases are expected to put a
OL,12,Fstrain on health services with
OL,13,Fanalysts predicting that 36,000 more
OL,14,Fwould be made by 2043.
OL,16,FHospital bed days may also rise by 30%.
OL,18,FA second report, the "multi-morbidity"
OL,19,Freport, refers to those who have more
OL,20,Fthan one long-term health condition.
